feat(scope): imperative summary in English

# Conventional Commits — LogPose
# type: feat | fix | docs | refactor | chore | build | ci | test | perf | revert
# scope (required): api | web | contracts | deps | ci | docs | root
#
# Examples:
#   feat(api): migrate posts and comments oRPC handlers
#   fix(web): correct login redirect after register
#   chore(deps): bump turbo catalog version
#
# Body (optional): explain why, not what. No period at end of subject.
